{"tid":1156202,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"[I/A]經典交友模擬遊戲戀愛盒子M","createTime":"2019-05-15T12:42:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-25T05:39:49.000Z","uid":130889,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"8c98bdf22ee68e77427ccdc09615d61148c63b64","tid":1156202,"uid":130889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T12:42:51.000Z","msg":"如果 15 年前你已經出生，那你一定聽過《戀愛盒子 Online》，由知名國產遊戲公司中華網龍研發，擁有獨特系統的交友模擬遊戲一時蔚為風潮，現在已確認將登上移動裝置，推出手遊版本《戀愛盒子M》。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n《戀愛盒子 Online》於 2004 年正式公測，一推出即擁有數十萬會員帳號、風靡萬千少男少女，即使 15 年過去仍讓許多玩家念念不忘，如何移植端遊感動，也成為這次手遊改編的主要重點。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.4gamers.com.tw/ckfinder/images/Panda/news/190321-lovebox-%20(1).JPG?versionId=DzKpRdzxrQ9b9SGh3Um_WpzpMUtEDUNr\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.4gamers.com.tw%2Fckfinder%2Fimages%2FPanda%2Fnews%2F190321-lovebox-%2520%281%29.JPG%3FversionId%3DDzKpRdzxrQ9b9SGh3Um_WpzpMUtEDUNr&h=e1a14e63&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.4gamers.com.tw/ckfinder/images/Panda/news/190321-lovebox-%20(2).jpg?versionId=ti_B1xTK6TT7HnRuiqHbwSeqWIiw8GFr\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.4gamers.com.tw%2Fckfinder%2Fimages%2FPanda%2Fnews%2F190321-lovebox-%2520%282%29.jpg%3FversionId%3Dti_B1xTK6TT7HnRuiqHbwSeqWIiw8GFr&h=097411cc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"38720846ab3d01ab872b2ca8f9ba011a4eeb655a","tid":1156202,"uid":40226,"like":7,"dislike":5,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T12:45:43.000Z","msg":"On9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d5dd56925346f4294e007a867a2f30c68087530","tid":1156202,"uid":239266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T16:08:30.000Z","msg":"今日有得下載了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n有興趣或者想搵返童年回憶可以下載玩吓<br />\n<br />\nAn:<br />\n<a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.chinesegamer.lbman&amp;fbclid=IwAR0YOTqUt_oOFY5ftNYANhxHxHOrgPeitto-6l8p3zFBnCym